answers.body_markdown:
This is the wrong way to run a program with an argument:    

    ProcessBuilder processBuilder = new ProcessBuilder(&quot;$python script.py&quot;);

You must pass the argument separately:

    ProcessBuilder processBuilder = new ProcessBuilder(&quot;$python&quot;, &quot;script.py&quot;);

